      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Atom Publishing Protocol (AtomPub) is an application-level protocol for publishing and editing Web resources.  The protocol is based on HTTP transfer of Atom-formatted representations.  The Atom format is documented in the Atom Syndication Format. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
